          <para styleclass="VariableName-small">Zero / Round / Copy / Paste contextual menu<text styleclass="Popup Box2">&#32;</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box">Right-click a Parameter-box to see this contextual menu.</para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="VariableName-small">Zero</text> - make the Parameter equal zero - if possible</para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="VariableName-small">Round</text> - make the Parameter a value exactly divisible by Spin-Increment</para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="VariableName-small">Copy</text> - replace Parameter with value in Clipboard</para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="VariableName-small">Paste</text> - copy the Parameter to the Clipboard</para>
